'''丹尼爾·戴爾·約翰斯頓'''（{{lang-en|Daniel Dale Johnston}}，{{bd|1961年|1月22日|2019年|9月11日|catIdx=Johnston}}<!-- 9月11日為遺體發現日，亦可能逝世於9月10日，各有來源-->）是一位美國創作歌手和視覺藝術家，他被認為是{{le|圈外人音樂|outsider music}}、[[低傳真度音樂|低傳真度音樂]]和[[另類搖滾|另類搖滾]]界中舉足輕重的人物<ref name="allmusic-bio"/><ref name="dazed-123"/>。他絕大多數的作品都是在自宅以[[卡式錄音帶|卡式錄音帶]]自行錄製的<ref name="AV2013"/>，而他的音樂因其「純粹」且「童趣」的特質而經常被引用。<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNamee|first1=David|title=The myth of Daniel Johnston's genius|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2009/aug/10/daniel-johnston|work={{link-en|The Guardian|TheGuardian.com}}|date=August 10, 2009|accessdate=2021-01-29|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126194844/http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2009/aug/10/daniel-johnston|dead-url=no}}</ref>

約翰斯頓生命中有很長一段時光都在精神病院中度過<ref name="AV2013"/>，而他也被診斷出患有[[躁鬱症|躁鬱症]]並為其所困<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Brook|first1=Pete|title=PHOTOGRAPHER SHOWS A DIFFERENT SIDE OF DANIEL JOHNSTON|journal=[[連線|連線]]|date=March 2012|url=https://www.wired.com/2012/03/photographer-shows-a-different-side-of-daniel-johnston/|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627034259/https://www.wired.com/2012/03/photographer-shows-a-different-side-of-daniel-johnston/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="allmusic-bio"/>。1980年代，他在[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]][[奧斯丁|奧斯丁]]的麥當勞工作，閒餘時則發送錄有自創音樂的錄音帶，因而在當時吸引當地不少支持者<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Hall|first1=Michael|title=He's Daniel Johnston, And He Was Gonna Be Famous|url=http://www.texasmonthly.com/articles/hes-daniel-johnston-and-he-was-gonna-be-famous/|journal=[[Texas_Monthly|Texas Monthly]]|date=February 2005|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031047/https://www.texasmonthly.com/articles/hes-daniel-johnston-and-he-was-gonna-be-famous/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在[[超脫樂團|超脫樂團]]主唱[[寇特·柯本|寇特·柯本]]穿著印有約翰斯頓1983年專輯《{{link-en|嗨，你好嗎|Hi, How Are You}}》封面的T恤的形象被大眾所知後，約翰斯頓在非主流音樂界的地位更上一層樓。<ref name="AV2013">{{cite web|last1=D'Angelo|first1=Mike|title=Is Daniel Johnston a great musician or a victim of hipster exploitation?|url=http://www.avclub.com/article/is-daniel-johnston-a-great-musician-or-a-victim-of-200584|website=[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]|date=December 5, 2013|accessdate=2021-01-29|archive-date=2017-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816193705/http://www.avclub.com/article/is-daniel-johnston-a-great-musician-or-a-victim-of-200584|dead-url=no}}</ref>

除了音樂以外，約翰斯頓還是位視覺藝術家，他的插畫作品已被展示在世界各地的許多畫廊之中。而他與精神疾病對抗的過程，也在2005年被拍成紀錄片《{{link-en|魔鬼與約翰斯頓|The Devil and Daniel Johnston}}》。約翰斯頓在2019年過世，死因疑似為心臟病發作。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/daniel-johnston-dead-883161/|title=Daniel Johnston, Cult Singer-Songwriter, Dead at 58|last1=Grow|first1=Kory|date=2019-09-11|website=Rolling Stone|language=en-US|access-date=2019-10-13|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210204559/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/daniel-johnston-dead-883161/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==早年==
約翰斯頓生於加利福尼亞州[[沙加緬度_(加利福尼亞州)|沙加緬度]]，在西維吉尼亞州{{link-en|新坎伯蘭縣 (西維吉尼亞州)|New Cumberland, West Virginia}}成長<ref name="RSOBIT">{{cite web |last1=Grow |first1=Kory |title=Daniel Johnston, Cult Singer-Songwriter, Dead at 58 |url=https://pitchfork.com/news/daniel-johnston-dead-at-58/ |website=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] |date=September 11, 2019 |access-date=September 11, 2019 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205070851/https://pitchfork.com/news/daniel-johnston-dead-at-58/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其雙親為威廉·戴爾·「比爾」·約翰斯頓（1922年生，2017年歿）和梅貝爾·露絲·沃伊爾絲·約翰斯頓（1923年生，2010年歿），是五個孩子中最小的。打從1970年代末起，約翰斯頓就靠著一台59美元的三洋單聲道錄音機錄製自己的音樂，形式包括歌唱、演奏鋼琴及和弦風琴<ref name="RSOBIT" />。從{{link-en|橡樹格倫高中|Oak Glen High School}}畢業後，約翰斯頓在德州的[[阿比林基督大學|阿比林基督大學]]待了幾個星期，接著就退學了。後來，他參與肯特州立大學東利物浦校區的藝術企劃，期間錄製了《{{link-en|痛苦之歌|Songs of Pain}}》和《{{link-en|更多痛苦之歌|More Songs of Pain}}》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hihowareyou.com/web/bio.htm|title=Hi, How Are You? Daniel Johnston – Biography|website=www.hihowareyou.com|accessdate=2021-01-29|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030093825/http://www.hihowareyou.com/web/bio.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==事業==
===1980年代至1990年代===
當約翰斯頓搬到德克薩斯州奧斯丁後，他開始習慣性地向他認識的人發送自己錄製的錄音帶，並因此吸引許多追隨者，更因此引起媒體關注<ref>{{cite news |title=Daniel Johnson, cult singer-songwriter, dies age 58 |url=https://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=12267070 |access-date=September 12, 2019 |newspaper=[[New_Zealand_Herald|New Zealand Herald]] |date=September 12, 2019 |archive-date=2020-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200310143342/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=12267070 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的現場演出備受關注和期待<ref>{{cite news |last=Black |first=Louis |url=http://www.austinchronicle.com/gyrobase/Issue/story?oid=oid:363536 |title=Genius and Jive: My roller-coaster relationship with Daniel Johnston Austin Screens |newspaper={{link-en|奧斯丁紀事|The Austin Chronicle}} |publisher=Austin Chronicle Corp. |location=Austin, Texas |date=May 5, 2006 |access-date=September 18, 2010 |archive-date=2012-09-01 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ALSuiahe?url=http://www.austinchronicle.com/screens/2006-05-05/363536/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他在當地的知名度及地位逐漸提高，使得[[音樂電視網|音樂電視網]]節目《The Cutting Edge》在1985年播出的一集節目中介紹了他的音樂，節目中給他的頭銜是來自奧斯丁「[[新真誠|新真誠]]」的音樂表演家。<ref>{{cite book|first=Barry|last=Shank|title=Dissonant Identities: The Rock'N'Roll Scene in Austin, Texas|publisher=[[Wesleyan_University_Press|Wesleyan University Press]]|location=Middleton, Connecticut|date=1994|isbn=978-0-8195-6276-0|pages=157–58|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=v79of-KXnfgC&q=%22The+Cutting+Edge%22&pg=PA157|via=[[Google圖書|Google圖書]]}}</ref>

1988年，約翰斯頓造訪紐約市，與音樂製作人{{link-en|克萊默 (音樂家)|Kramer (musician)|馬克·克萊默}}一起在克萊默的噪音紐約工作室錄製唱片《{{link-en|1990 (丹尼爾·約翰斯頓專輯)|1990 (Daniel Johnston album)|1990}}》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kramershimmy.com |title=kramershimmy home |publisher=Kramershimmy.com |access-date=September 18, 2010 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126081615/http://www.kramershimmy.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RSOBIT" />。這是約翰斯頓第一次在專業的錄音環境中製作音樂，距離他當年頭一次發送自製的卡式錄音帶的日子，已經經歷了十年之久。在製作完《1990》之後，他的心理健康狀況進一步惡化<ref name="PFOBIT">{{cite web |last1=Blais-Billie |first1=Braudie |title=Daniel Johnston Dead at 58 |url=https://pitchfork.com/news/daniel-johnston-dead-at-58/ |website=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork]] |publisher=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]] |location=Chicago, Illinois |date=September 11, 2019 |access-date=September 11, 2019 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205070851/https://pitchfork.com/news/daniel-johnston-dead-at-58/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1989年，約翰斯頓和{{link-en|Half Japanese|Half Japanese}}樂團的歌手{{link-en|杰德·菲爾|Jad Fair}}合作發行專輯《{{link-en|It's Spooky|It's Spooky}}》<ref>{{cite web |last1=Schreiber |first1=Ryan |title=It's Spooky review |url=https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/2957-its-spooky/ |website=[[Pitchfork_(website)|Pitchfork]] |publisher=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]] |location=Chicago, Illinois |date=June 19, 2001 |access-date=September 11, 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128025857/https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/2957-its-spooky/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1990年，約翰斯頓在奧斯丁的音樂節上演出，結束後準備回到西維吉尼亞。他在回程時搭乘他父親駕駛的雙人座私人飛機，期間思覺失調症狀發作，讓約翰斯頓相信自己是[[鬼馬小精靈|鬼馬小精靈]]，他把飛機的鑰匙拔下並扔到外面。所幸他的父親比爾是前美國空軍飛行員，儘管「下方除了樹之外還是樹」，比爾還是成功地讓飛機迫降，雖然飛機被毀了，但父子倆只受了輕傷，由於此一事件，約翰斯頓被非自願地送到精神病院。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2006/apr/02/metallica | work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]] | location=London, England | title=Sean O'Hagan on Daniel Johnston | first=Sean | last=O'Hagan | date=April 2, 2006 | access-date=March 15, 2011 | archive-date=2021-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209161403/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2006/apr/02/metallica | dead-url=no }}</ref>

在音樂記者{{link-en|艾佛里特·真實|Everett True}}拍下了[[超脫樂團|超脫樂團]]主唱[[寇特·柯本|寇特·柯本]]穿著印有約翰斯頓1983年專輯《{{link-en|嗨，你好嗎|Hi, How Are You}}》封面圖片的T恤後，大眾對約翰斯頓的興趣也增加不少<ref name="RSOBIT" />，寇特·柯本在1993年的日記中提到自己最喜歡的專輯是《{{link-en|Yip/Jump Music|Yip/Jump Music}}》<ref name="joyfulnoiserecordings.com">{{cite web |title=Top 50 by Nirvana [MIXTAPE] |url=http://www.joyfulnoiserecordings.com/journal/top-50-by-nirvana/ |access-date=May 8, 2013 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018034220/http://www.joyfulnoiserecordings.com/journal/top-50-by-nirvana/ |archive-date=2014-10-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管約翰斯頓身在精神病院之中，但還是有許多公司想簽下他，他回絕[[厄勒克特拉唱片|厄勒克特拉唱片]]的合約，因為[[金屬製品|金屬製品]]也在該公司旗下，而他堅信金屬製品的成員都像[[撒但|撒但]]一樣會傷害他<ref name="PFOBIT" />，而這段期間，他還解雇了長期擔任自己經紀人的傑夫·塔塔科夫（Jeff Tartakov）<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.azcentral.com/ent/movies/articles/0811johnston0811.html | work=[[The_Arizona_Republic|The Arizona Republic]] |publisher=[[Gannett|Gannett]]| location=Phoenix, Arizona| title=The Devil and Daniel Johnston | first=Michael | last=Senft | date=August 11, 2006 | access-date=March 15, 2011}}</ref>。最後他在1994年2月與[[大西洋唱片|大西洋唱片]]簽約，在9月發行《{{link-en|Fun (專輯)|Fun (album)|Fun}}》，該專輯的製作人為{{link-en|屁眼衝浪者|Butthole Surfers}}的{{link-en|保羅·利里|Paul Leary}}<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2005/aug/20/edinburghfilmfestival2005.popandrock | work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]] | location=London, England | title=Personal demons | first=John | last=Robinson | date=August 20, 2005 | access-date=April 30, 2010 | archive-date=2021-02-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212020314/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2005/aug/20/edinburghfilmfestival2005.popandrock | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此專輯在商業上並未成功，1996年6月，大西洋唱片解除了與約翰斯頓的合約。<ref name="PFOBIT" />

[[File:Hi_How_Are_You_Austin_2005.jpg|thumb]]

1993年，德克薩斯州奧斯丁的Sound Exchange唱片行委請約翰斯頓畫一張壁畫，主題是《嗨，你好嗎？》專輯封面上的青蛙（此蛙又稱「Jeremiah the Innocent」）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rejectedunknown.com/art/public/bajafresh.htm |title=Baja Fresh Hi How Are You frog mural |website=Rejectedunknown.com |date=January 6, 2004 |access-date=July 9, 2012 |archive-date=2019-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191027234113/http://rejectedunknown.com/art/public/bajafresh.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2003年，唱片行關門大吉，該建築物也一直空置，直到2004年，美國一家連鎖墨西哥燒烤品牌{{link-en|Baja Fresh|Baja Fresh}}取得所有權，並決定拆除畫有該壁畫的牆，在當地民眾說服分店經理後，該店決定保留壁畫的完整性<ref>{{cite web|first=Dan|last=Solomon|url=http://www.texasobserver.org/dateline/the-peoples-frog|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629135819/http://www.texasobserver.org/dateline/the-peoples-frog|archive-date=2011-06-29|title=The People's Frog|newspaper=[[The_Texas_Observer|The Texas Observer]]|publisher=Texas Democracy Foundation|location=Austin, Texas|date=November 10, 2010|access-date=July 9, 2012|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年，該建物開設了一家泰式餐廳，餐廳名為「Thai, How Are You」（泰，你好啊）<ref>{{cite news |last1=Hoffberger |first1=Chase |title=Landmark Daniel Johnston mural gets a touch-up |url=https://www.austinchronicle.com/daily/music/2013-08-28/thai-how-are-you/ |access-date=September 12, 2019 |newspaper=[[Austin_Chronicle|Austin Chronicle]] |publisher=Austin Chronicle Corp. |location=Austin, Texas |date=August 28, 2013 |archive-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203083219/https://www.austinchronicle.com/daily/music/2013-08-28/thai-how-are-you/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，餐廳在2020年1月歇業，而該建物也閒置至今。

===2000年代===
2004年，約翰斯頓發行了雙碟專輯《{{link-en|The Late Great Daniel Johnston: Discovered Covered|The Late Great Daniel Johnston: Discovered Covered}}》，首張唱片為翻唱其它藝術家的歌曲，對象包括[[湯姆·威茲|湯姆·威茲]]、[[貝克_(歌手)|貝克]]、{{link-en|電視電台樂團|TV on the Radio}}、{{link-en|杰德·菲爾|Jad Fair}}、[[Eels|Eels]]、{{link-en|明眸樂團|Bright Eyes (band)}}、{{link-en|卡爾文·詹森 (音樂家)|Calvin Johnson (musician)|卡爾文·詹森}}、[[俏妞的死亡計程車|俏妞的死亡計程車]]、{{link-en|Sparklehorse|Sparklehorse}}、{{link-en|水星逆轉|Mercury Rev}}、{{link-en|烈火紅唇|The Flaming Lips}}和{{link-en|星光薄荷|Starlight Mints}}，第二張唱片收錄約翰斯頓創作的歌曲<ref>{{cite web |last1=Moore |first1=David |title=Discovered, Covered:The Late, Great Daniel Johnston |url=https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/4283-discovered-covered-the-late-great-daniel-johnston-compilation-and-tribute/ |website=[[Pitchfork_(website)|Pitchfork]] |publisher=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]] |location=Chicago, Illinois |date=September 23, 2004 |access-date=September 12, 2019 |archive-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203011829/https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/4283-discovered-covered-the-late-great-daniel-johnston-compilation-and-tribute/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2005年，德克薩斯州的劇院公司{{link-en|煉獄新郎製作公司|Infernal Bridegroom Productions}}獲得了Multi-Arts Production基金會的贊助，與約翰斯頓合作，以他的音樂製作了一齣搖滾歌劇《Speeding Motorcycle》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mapfund.org/grant_59.html |title=Infernal Bridegroom Productions |publisher=MAP Fund |access-date=July 9, 2012 |archive-date=2017-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929044203/http://www.mapfund.org/grant_59.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[File:Daniel_Johnston_at_Emos_1.jpg|thumb]]

2006年，電影導演{{link-en|傑夫·費爾傑|Jeff Feuerzeig}}發行了紀錄片《{{link-en|魔鬼與約翰斯頓|The Devil and Daniel Johnston}}》，此片製作時間長達四年，整理了約翰斯頓（在某些情況下也包括其他人）多年來錄製的大量紀錄，也描述他的生活及音樂<ref>{{cite web |last1=Itzkoff |first1=Dave |author-link=Dave Itzkoff |title=Daniel, You're a Star: SPIN's 2006 Interview With Daniel Johnston's Documentarian |url=https://www.spin.com/2019/09/daniel-johnston-documentary-interview/ |website=[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]] |publisher=[[SpinMedia|SpinMedia]] |location=San Francisco, California |date=September 11, 2019 |access-date=September 12, 2019 |archive-date=2021-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202083444/https://www.spin.com/2019/09/daniel-johnston-documentary-interview/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此電影在2005年的[[日舞影展|日舞影展]]中獲得導演獎，並獲得一片好評<ref name="GUOBIT">{{cite news |last1=Beaumont-Thomas |first1=Ben |title=Daniel Johnston, cult US indie songwriter, dies aged 58 |url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/sep/11/daniel-johnston-cult-us-indie-songwriter-dies-aged-58 |access-date=September 12, 2019 |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=September 11, 2019 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208105304/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/sep/11/daniel-johnston-cult-us-indie-songwriter-dies-aged-58 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影還啟發了人們對於約翰斯頓的作品的興趣，也增加了他作為巡迴演出的藝術家的聲望。2006年，約翰斯頓的唱片公司Eternal Yip Eye Music發行了他的首張唱片合輯《Welcome to My World》。<ref>{{cite web |first=Colin |last=Stutz |url=http://www.filter-mag.com/news/interior.3145.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061223035358/http://www.filter-mag.com/news/interior.3145.html |archive-date=2006-12-23 |title=The News and Daniel Johnston |website=Filter-Mag.com |date=April 14, 2006 |access-date=July 9, 2012 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

往後幾年之間，約翰斯頓在世界各地頻繁地巡迴演出，持續引起媒體關注。他的作品曾於2006年和2008年在倫敦的{{link-en|水族館l-13|The Aquarium L-13|水族館畫廊}}、紐約的克萊門汀畫廊、{{link-en|利物浦雙年展|Liverpool Biennial}}等場地中展出<ref>{{cite web |last1=Ingvaldsen |first1=Torsten |title=Prodigious Indie Rock Musician & Artist Daniel Johnston Has Passed Away at 58 |url=https://hypebeast.com/2019/9/daniel-johnston-indie-rock-musician-artist-dead-aged-58 |website=Hypebeast |date=September 12, 2019 |access-date=September 12, 2019 |archive-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203050152/https://hypebeast.com/2019/9/daniel-johnston-indie-rock-musician-artist-dead-aged-58 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2009年，他的作品在[[沙加緬度_(加利福尼亞州)|沙加緬度]]的邊緣畫廊「愛的博物館」展出<ref>{{cite web|title=Daniel Johnston, Museum of Love|url=https://www.yelp.com/events/sacramento-daniel-johnston-museum-of-love|website=yelp.com|access-date=January 12, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822053432/https://www.yelp.com/events/sacramento-daniel-johnston-museum-of-love|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年，約翰斯頓的哥哥兼經紀人狄克·約翰斯頓表示「有部關於約翰斯頓在生活與音樂方面的電影，預定在2011年發行」<ref name="chronicle">{{cite news|first=Austin|last=Powell|title=Off the Record: Music News|newspaper=[[The_Austin_Chronicle|The Austin Chronicle]]|publisher=Austin Chronicle Corp.|location=Austin, Texas|url=http://www.austinchronicle.com/gyrobase/Issue/column?oid=oid%3A681411|date=October 3, 2008|accessdate=2021-01-29|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229211852/http://www.austinchronicle.com/gyrobase/Issue/column?oid=oid%3A681411|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他還表示與[[匡威|匡威]]展開合作，將推出丹尼爾·約翰斯頓的簽名鞋系列<ref name="chronicle" />。只是過沒多久，狄克·約翰斯頓就表示匡威終止了該項企畫<ref>{{cite web |url=http://monsterfresh.com/2009/06/16/daniel-johnston-converse-shoes-photos-unreleased/#more-3588 |title=Unreleased Daniel Johnston Converse All-Stars |publisher=MonsterFresh.com |access-date=September 18, 2010 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109001832/http://www.monsterfresh.com/2009/06/16/daniel-johnston-converse-shoes-photos-unreleased/#more-3588 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年初，限量發行了一款四色的Jeremiah the Innocent小塑像<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/daniel-johnstons-frog-jeremiah-now-a-collectors-item-20080625|title=Daniel Johnston's Frog Jeremiah: Now a Collector's Item|accessdate=2021-01-29|archive-date=2017-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107222520/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/daniel-johnstons-frog-jeremiah-now-a-collectors-item-20080625|dead-url=no}}</ref>，下半年，Adjustable製作公司發行約翰斯頓首張音樂會DVD《{{link-en|天使與丹尼爾·約翰斯頓 - 聯合教堂演唱會|The Angel and Daniel Johnston – Live at the Union Chapel}}》，收錄他在2007年7月12日於[[伊斯靈頓協和禮拜堂|伊斯靈頓協和禮拜堂]]的演出。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.prlog.org/10134907-the-angel-and-daniel-johnston-live-at-the-union-chapel.html |title=The Angel And Daniel Johnston – Live at the Union Chapel |publisher=Prlog.org |date=October 30, 2008 |access-date=September 18, 2010 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306134244/https://www.prlog.org/10134907-the-angel-and-daniel-johnston-live-at-the-union-chapel.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>


2009年10月6日，Eternal Yip Eye Music發行了《{{link-en|Is and Always Was|Is and Always Was}}》<ref>{{cite web |last1=Abebe |first1=Nitsuh |title=Is and Always Was |url=https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/13589-is-and-always-was/ |website=[[Pitchfork_(website)|Pitchfork]] |publisher=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]] |location=Chicago, Illinois |date=October 16, 2009 |access-date=September 12, 2019 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126100448/http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/13589-is-and-always-was/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2009年，{{link-en|所有明天的派對音樂節|All Tomorrow's Parties (festival)}}官方宣布，[[馬特·格朗寧|馬特·格朗寧]]選擇約翰斯頓參加他在2010年5月於英格蘭[[邁恩希德|邁恩希德]]策畫的音樂節活動<ref>{{cite web |title=ATP 2010: Curated By Matt Groening @ Butlin's Holiday Centre, Minehead, UK |url=https://www.stereogum.com/368301/atp-2010-curated-by-matt-groening-butlins-holiday-centre-minehead-uk/photo/ |website=Stereogum |access-date=September 12, 2019 |archive-date=2018-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180728081026/https://www.stereogum.com/368301/atp-2010-curated-by-matt-groening-butlins-holiday-centre-minehead-uk/photo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同年，Dr. Fun Fun和Smashing Studios聯合開發了一款運行於[[iPhone|iPhone]]的第三人稱[[平台遊戲|平台遊戲]]《{{link-en|嗨，你好嗎 (電子遊戲)|Hi, How Are You (video game)|嗨，你好嗎}}》，此遊戲的機制類似1981年的街機遊戲《[[青蛙過河|青蛙過河]]》，並使用了約翰斯頓的音樂和畫作。儘管約翰斯頓不欣賞iPhone，但他還是在遊戲開發期間參與試玩，也表示自己喜歡這款遊戲。<ref>{{cite news|first=Randy|last=Kenny|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/09/29/arts/design/29john.html?_r=3&ref=arts|title=Work of Daniel Johnston, Texas Artist, Inspires Video Game|newspaper=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|date=September 28, 2009|access-date=October 1, 2009|archive-date=2020-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115053617/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/09/29/arts/design/29john.html?_r=3&ref=arts|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===2010年代===
2012年3月13日，約翰斯頓在[[西南偏南|西南偏南]]發行了他的首部漫畫書《Space Ducks – An Infinite Comic Book of Musical Greatness》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lambiek.net/artists/j/johnston_daniel.htm|title=Daniel Johnston|website=lambiek.net|accessdate=2021-01-29|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203084557/https://www.lambiek.net/artists/j/johnston_daniel.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，該書由[[Boom!工作室|Boom!工作室]]出版。此書與他的專輯《Space Ducks》及一款iOS應用程式緊密關聯<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hihowareyou.com/news/posts/14 |title=Official Press Release for SPACE DUCKS |publisher=HiHowAreYou.com |accessdate=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206224335/https://www.hihowareyou.com/news/posts/14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。約翰斯頓和[[Supreme|Supreme]]公司合作，推出許多印有他的畫作的服裝和各種配件。<ref>{{Cite web|first=Jenn|last=Pelly|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/46815-daniel-johnston-designs-shirts-for-supreme/|title=Daniel Johnston Designs Shirts for Supreme|website=[[Pitchfork|Pitchfork]]|publisher=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]|location=Chicago, Illinois|language=en|date=June 12, 2012|access-date=May 11, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013707/https://pitchfork.com/news/46815-daniel-johnston-designs-shirts-for-supreme/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年3月1日，布魯克林的攝影師金正宣布將與約翰斯頓一起展開巡迴展覽計畫，計畫名稱為「丹尼爾·約翰斯頓：登場」，這項合作計畫始於2008年，當時金正在德克薩斯州{{link-en|沃勒 (德克薩斯州)|Waller, Texas|沃勒}}初次見到並開始拍攝約翰斯頓，而約翰斯頓正在回家的路上<ref name="DAZED">{{cite web |last1=Hagi |first1=Ella |title=Daniel Johnston's lo-fi life |url=https://www.dazeddigital.com/photography/article/16171/1/lo-fi-life |website=Dazed |date=24 May 2013 |access-date=12 September 2019 |archive-date=2020-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200604045054/https://www.dazeddigital.com/photography/article/16171/1/lo-fi-life |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年3月13日，與此計畫相關的攝影集付梓，書中包含有關約翰斯頓這五年來的資料<ref name="DAZED" />。在[[西南偏南|西南偏南]]音樂節的開幕式中，由前{{link-en|水星逆轉|Mercury Rev}}成員{{link-en|傑森·賽巴斯汀·盧索|Jason Sebastian Russo}}率領了一齣表演，特別向約翰斯頓致敬<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.austinchronicle.com/photos/daniel-johnston-here-book-release-and-opening/2/|title=Daniel Johnston "here" Book Release & Opening|newspaper=[[The_Austin_Chronicle|The Austin Chronicle]]|publisher=Austin Chronicle Corp.|location=Austin, Texas|date=March 13, 2013|accessdate=2021-01-29|archive-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822095517/https://www.austinchronicle.com/photos/daniel-johnston-here-book-release-and-opening/2/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.wired.com/rawfile/2012/03/photographer-shows-a-different-side-of-daniel-johnston/ |title=Photographer Shows a Different Side of Daniel |magazine=[[連線|連線]] |publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]] |location=New York City |date=March 28, 2012 |accessdate=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2014-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114005234/http://www.wired.com/rawfile/2012/03/photographer-shows-a-different-side-of-daniel-johnston/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第二場展出於2013年5月和6月在倫敦舉行，約翰斯頓在該場展出中進行特別演出，而英國團體Charlie Boyer and the Voyeurs和{{link-en|悲鳴樂團|Klaxons}}成員斯特凡·海爾普林進行致敬演出<ref name="dazed-123">{{cite web |url=http://www.dazeddigital.com/photography/article/16171/1/lo-fi-life |title=Daniel Johnston's Lo-Fi Life |publisher=DAZED Digital |date=May 24, 2013 |accessdate=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2020-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200604045054/https://www.dazeddigital.com/photography/article/16171/1/lo-fi-life |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.prote.in/en/feed/2013/06/daniel-johnston-secret-show#.Uob7J42heuU |title=Daniel Johnston Secret Show |publisher=Protein UK |date=June 3, 2013 |accessdate=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2017-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171102020633/https://www.prote.in/en/feed/2013/06/daniel-johnston-secret-show#.Uob7J42heuU |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

之後展覽移師紐約市，2013年10月10日，{{link-en|形而上合唱團|Spiritualized}}的{{link-en|傑森·皮爾斯|Jason Pierce}}主持展覽開幕典禮，傑森·皮爾斯和{{link-en|The Swell Season|The Swell Season}}兼[[The_Frames|The Frames]]成員{{link-en|格倫·韓薩|Glen Hansard}}進行致敬演出。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.brooklynvegan.com/archives/2013/10/j_spaceman_glen.html |title=Daniel Johnston Book Event |publisher=Brooklyn Vegan |date=October 10, 2013 |accessdate=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2016-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204091342/http://www.brooklynvegan.com/archives/2013/10/j_spaceman_glen.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gettyimages.com/Search/Search.aspx?contractUrl=2&language=en-US&family=editorial&assetType=image&mt=photography&p=Daniel+Johnston+NYC+Pop+Up |title=Daniel Johnston NYC Pop Up |publisher=Getty |date=October 10, 2013 |accessdate=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811102704/http://www.gettyimages.com/Search/Search.aspx?contractUrl=2&language=en-US&family=editorial&assetType=image&mt=photography&p=Daniel+Johnston+NYC+Pop+Up |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年11月，《嗨，你好嗎丹尼爾·約翰斯頓》發行，這是部關於約翰斯頓生活的簡短紀錄片，片中由《{{link-en|阿奇最終計畫|Archie's Final Project}}》的{{link-en|加百列禮拜日|Gabriel Sunday}}飾演1983年的約翰斯頓，而約翰斯頓本人飾演2015年的他自己。此片的執行製作人包括[[拉娜·德芮|拉娜·德芮]]和[[麥克·米勒|麥克·米勒]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Hi How Are You Daniel Johnston|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4977790/|website=IMDB.com|access-date=January 12, 2017|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921133212/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4977790/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.twentyfourbit.com/post/457060631/daniel-johnston-biopic-my-suicide-soundtrack-more |title=Daniel Johnston Biopic, My Suicide Soundtrack, & More |publisher=TwentyFourBit |date=March 18, 2010 |access-date=September 18, 2010 |archive-date=2012-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306200207/http://www.twentyfourbit.com/post/457060631/daniel-johnston-biopic-my-suicide-soundtrack-more |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年7月，約翰斯頓宣布將不再進行現場演出，並在該年秋季進行了五日的告別巡迴演出<ref name="finaltour">{{cite web|last1=Kim|first1=Michelle|title=Daniel Johnston Announces Final Tour|website=[[Pitchfork_(website)|Pitchfork]]|publisher=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]|location=Chicago, Illinois|url=http://pitchfork.com/news/daniel-johnston-announces-final-tour|date=July 26, 2017|access-date=July 26, 2017|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109031429/https://pitchfork.com/news/daniel-johnston-announces-final-tour/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在巡迴演出的每一站，約翰斯頓都會和受他音樂影響的樂團合作演出：在紐奧良是{{link-en|典藏大廳爵士樂團|Preservation Hall Jazz Band}}、在費城是{{link-en|區域樂團|The Districts}}和{{link-en|現代棒球樂團|Modern Baseball}}、在芝加哥是和{{link-en|傑夫·特維迪|Jeff Tweedy}}合作，在波特蘭和溫哥華是和{{link-en|殺戮工具合唱團|Built to Spill}}合作。<ref name="finaltour"/>

== 逝世 ==
2019年，約翰斯頓因原因不明的腎臟問題而住院，在他出院後的隔日，9月11日，他被發現逝世於德克薩斯州{{link-en|沃勒 (德克薩斯州)|Waller, Texas|沃勒}}的自宅中，死因疑為心臟病發作，死亡時間推測為10日或11日的深夜。<ref>{{cite news|url = https://www.cbsnews.com/news/daniel-johnston-died-austin-singer-songwriter-artist-dead-age-58-cause-of-death-unknown-2019-09-12/|title = Daniel Johnston, Austin singer-songwriting icon, has died at 58|work = [[CBS新聞|CBS新聞]]|publisher = [[CBS公司|CBS公司]]|location = New York City|date = September 12, 2019|access-date = September 15, 2019|archive-date = 2021-02-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210208084852/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/daniel-johnston-died-austin-singer-songwriter-artist-dead-age-58-cause-of-death-unknown-2019-09-12/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Curtin|first1=Kevin|title=Austin Songwriting Genius Daniel Johnston Dead at 58|url=https://www.austinchronicle.com/daily/music/2019-09-11/austin-singer-songwriter-daniel-johnston-dead-at-58/|newspaper=[[Austin_Chronicle|Austin Chronicle]]|publisher=Austin Chronicle Corp.|location=Austin, Texas|date=September 11, 2019|access-date=September 11, 2019|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912081006/https://www.austinchronicle.com/daily/music/2019-09-11/austin-singer-songwriter-daniel-johnston-dead-at-58/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url = https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/11/arts/music/daniel-johnston-dead.html|title = Daniel Johnston, Enigmatic Singer-Songwriter, Is Dead at 58|last = Sisario|first = Ben|date = September 11, 2019|access-date = September 11, 2019|work = [[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|publisher = [[New_York_Times_Company|New York Times Company]]|location = New York City|archive-url = https://archive.today/20190912051602/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/11/arts/music/daniel-johnston-dead.html|archive-date = 2019-09-12|dead-url = no}}</ref>

